title: Tourach's Gate
text: Enchant land you controlSacrifice a Thrull: Put three time counters on Tourach's Gate.At the beginning of your upkeep, remove a time counter from Tourach's Gate. If there are no time counters on Tourach's Gate, sacrifice it.Tap enchanted land: Attacking creatures you control get +2/-1 until end of turn. Activate this ability only if enchanted land is untapped.
